Crusher
de_crush

Map by MarkQ/Turd Furguson

Storm's a brewing in the West Newfoundland High Quality Box and Explosive Storage building. Two big, angry groups
of dirty cussin' mofos are about to get down with a brawl the likes only de_dust has seen in a long time. Tonight,
some blood's gonna be splattered on the concrete and some teeth are gonna be bereft of a jaw. IT'S GO TIME. 
Fortunately for us, we got ringside seats for this battle of a millenium, but the map's a bit out of date. 

HAVE FUN ANYWAYS

3rd Release, HDR-Enabled

Bot pathing fixed
